data.description: Raised ranch in the city limits! Underground pool with 3 bedroom, 2 full bath with open floor plan that has the living room and dining room under a vaulted ceiling. Laundry room on the main floor, double sinks in both baths. Separate large master suite with a walk-in closet. Two car drive in basement.  Full length covered front porch and a back deck to enjoy the beautiful mountain views.
